jacdac.RainGaugeReg.Precipitation:
Read-only mm u16.16 (uint32_t). Total precipitation recorded so far.
* ```
const [precipitation] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u16.16")
```
jacdac.RainGaugeReg.PrecipitationPrecisi:
Constant mm u16.16 (uint32_t). Typically the amount of rain needed for tipping the bucket.
* ```
const [precipitationPrecision] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u16.16")
```
modules.RainGaugeClient: Measures the amount of liquid precipitation over an area in a predefined period of time.
modules.RainGaugeClient.onPrecipitationC: Run code when the precipitation changes by the given threshold value.
modules.RainGaugeClient.precipitationPre: Typically the amount of rain needed for tipping the bucket.
